## About Me Hi everyone! My name is Cindy and I am a Senior Business Analyst based in Boston, MA. I reside with my long term partner and my Bichon Frise Pup named Kylo. When I’m not engaging in analytical work or graduate school, I can be found at a the gym, more specifically, taking barre. I am an avid barre lover and am super passionate about the excercise. Aside from being a barre baddie, I enjoy spending quality time with my very LARGE family and eating good food.
## Education Graduated from Bridgewater State University Bachelors Degree in BioChemistry
Currently enrolled at Boston University Masters in Applied Business Analytics
